Usage: deleteFiller [-help] [-area <box>] [-cell <cellList>] [-keepFixed] [-inst <instName> | -prefix <prefix> ]

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-area <box>          # (box, optional)
-cell <cellList>     # (string, optional)
-inst <instName>     # (string, optional)
-keepFixed           # (bool, optional)
-prefix <prefix>     # (string, optional)